# Cursor Rules (legacy)

Newer Cursor versions read `.cursor/rules/*.mdc` instead of this file; see
[`.cursor/rules/agents.mdc`](.cursor/rules/agents.mdc). This file is kept for
backward compatibility.

All canonical operating procedures, commands, conventions, and rules for AI agents
working in this repository are defined in **[AGENTS.md](AGENTS.md)**. Read and
follow it before performing any task.
